## Educational Content License (Restrictive)

### German Vocabulary Dataset (`src/data/initialWords.json`)

The German vocabulary dataset contained in this project, including but not limited to:
- German words and their translations
- Example sentences and their meanings
- Curated vocabulary collections
- Language learning content structure

Is protected under the following additional terms:

**PERMITTED USES:**
- ✅ Personal learning and education
- ✅ Academic research and study
- ✅ Non-commercial educational projects
- ✅ Contributing improvements back to this project
- ✅ Creating derivatives for personal use

**PROHIBITED USES:**
- ❌ Commercial use without explicit written permission
- ❌ Redistribution in commercial language learning applications
- ❌ Selling or monetizing the vocabulary content
- ❌ Creating competing commercial products using this dataset
- ❌ Removing attribution or copyright notices
- ❌ Claiming ownership of the vocabulary compilation

### Commercial Use Permission

If you wish to use the vocabulary dataset for commercial purposes, please contact:
- Email: [Your Email]
- GitHub: @atj393

We are open to licensing arrangements for legitimate educational businesses and applications.

### Attribution Requirements

Any use of this vocabulary dataset must include clear attribution:

```
German vocabulary dataset courtesy of Deutsch Flasher project
by Alexis T. Jackson (https://github.com/atj393/Deutsch-Flasher-ScrollView)
```

### Enforcement

Violation of these terms may result in:
- Takedown requests
- Legal action for copyright infringement
- Loss of permission to use any part of this project

### Why This License?

This project represents significant effort in:
- Curating 2000+ high-quality German vocabulary words
- Creating contextual example sentences
- Developing intelligent spaced repetition algorithms
- Building a complete learning platform

We want to encourage learning and open-source contribution while protecting against commercial exploitation of our educational content.

